                    <comment id="12626142" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Wed, 27 Aug 2008 15:46:58 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I just tried updating Solr... I guess this isn&apos;t so backward compatible (code-wise) because of the package change?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;    [javac] f:\code\solr\src\java\org\apache\solr\analysis\EnglishPorterFilterFactory.java:78: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;package&lt;/span&gt; net.sf.snowball.ext does not exist
    [javac]   &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; net.sf.snowball.ext.EnglishStemmer stemmer;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Oh, nevermind... SnowballFilter should be the public interface that this is accessed through.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
